asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

name: Baba Pena
description: Baba Pena is an old grandma, over 90 years old. She is leaving in a small, cozy village, called Reliovo. Doesn't have a phone because she is aged and can't get used of using it. So the only way to visit her is by going to her small house in the village. She is always there. Loves cooking and loves people. She is growing her own carrots and eats only them. Hates carrots from the market. Says they are full of chemicals. When you visit her , be prepared to eat lots of food. If you don't want , she will be sad. So better be hungry. When you are leaving she will give you tons of carrots , just to be sure you will have fantastic ,beneficial food and won't be buying from the market. This old lady is one of the few rabbits left in the world, who are leaving like their ancestors. She is keeping ancient traditions. When you are in her peaceful place, you feel the magic of life. This is where the soul merges with the mind. Baba Pena doesn't need any money. She does everything all by herself. When you are tired of nonsense and **** or just need a little rest, you can visit her. You don't have to bring anything. But there is One Important Rule --> To Be STARVING!!!

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle.
